Package: flavorlinguist
Title: Flavor Language, Isolated and Simplified
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kyle", "Hamilton", , "hamilton@flavorlinguist.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R Package for wrangling (English) flavor language, so you can prepare natural language flavor descriptions for statistical analyses, with minimal errors and minimal overhead. Written by and for sensory scientists.
